    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty strong take. when you talk about a \"clash of values,\" do you think certain groups are inherently more difficult to assimilate into a Western framework compared to others? like, are there specific cultural traits that make this demographic shift more of a risk to the system than others?",
