      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so you're saying the demographic change isn't just about numbers, but about the specific nature of the people coming in. if this trend continues and the \"dominant culture\" keeps getting pushed out like you mentioned, do you think we're looking at a point of no return for the US as we know it? basically, is the end of \"Western\" America inevitable if these specific groups become the majority?",
